[[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] is to be reminded that it has no name. --It constantly knows this fact.-- Constant reminders are hereby classified as vital to the Foundation's continued directives.

[[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] must be located. It must be brought to justice.
[[/hcell]]
