[[hcell style="border: 1px solid #f3f3f3; font-weight: normal; padding: 0.25em;"]]
[[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] is an entity without identity. The entity has no name. [[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] is often characterized as --being cruel--.

Under no circumstances is [[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] permitted to live. Allowing it to indulge in basic human interaction or decency will result in immediate --K-Class Scenario-- --Apollyon-Level Containment Breach-- an instantaneous formation of a singularity, capable of destroying our solar system and nearby star system Alpha Centauri, located 4.37 light-years away from our Sun.
[[/hcell]]
