[[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] is you, the reader.
[[include :scp-wiki:component:listusers-3 users="."]]

[[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] is every registered Wikidot, Facebook, Instagram, and Snapchat user. It is none of these. [[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] includes [[*user Moto42]], [[*user Dr Dan]], and [[*user billith]]. It is not --[[*user Eberstrom]] and [[*user The Administrator]]--.
