[[hcell style="border: 1px solid #f3f3f3; font-weight: normal; padding: 0.25em;"]]
[[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] is solely responsible for the complete destruction of every organism that it has affected. [[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] is fully capable of ascertaining who it has harmed. [[span class="name"]]SCP-9615[[/span]] is to be obliterated for its previous actions. It must suffer indefinitely for its vile treatment of others without a name.

It does not deserve your sympathy.
[[/hcell]]
